#. Title = APT ORB / wearing fancy loafers
#. Description = Putting the shoes on gives a one time +1 to Indirect Modes of Taxation, you capitalist swine.
#. Actor = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000021000009C9"
msgid "You're right, beautiful things do make people happy..."
msgstr ""
"Du hast recht. Schöne Dinge machen Menschen glücklich …"

#. Title = APT ORB / wearing fancy loafers
#. Description = Putting the shoes on gives a one time +1 to Indirect Modes of Taxation, you capitalist swine.
#. Actor = Rhetoric
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x010000060001BB7A"
msgid "They're either a gateway drug -- or a booster pack -- to get you *deeper* into free market ideology."
msgstr ""
"Sie sind entweder eine Einstiegsdroge – oder ein Verstärker –, um dich <i>tiefer</i> in die Ideologie des freien Marktes hineinzuziehen."

#. Title = APT ORB / wearing fancy loafers
#. Description = Putting the shoes on gives a one time +1 to Indirect Modes of Taxation, you capitalist swine.
#. Actor = Savoir Faire
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000021000009C2"
msgid "Mm, the luxury of fine things. Just look at those black monk straps! After spending an entire day hustling, who's to say that you *didn't* deserve a pair of ridiculously expensive shoes on your tired feet?"
msgstr ""
"Hm, der Luxus edler Dinge. Sieh dir nur diese schwarzen Monkstraps an! Nach einem harten Tag voller Geschäftemacherei kann dir niemand erzählen, dass deine müden Füße kein Paar absurd teurer Schuhe verdienen."

#. Title = APT ORB / wearing fancy loafers
#. Description = Putting the shoes on gives a one time +1 to Indirect Modes of Taxation, you capitalist swine.
#. Actor = Savoir Faire
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000021000009D7"
msgid "Remember, when they come to take it *away* from you -- you *worked* for those shoes. Whether you like it or not, wearing these shoes has made you more liberal -- *ultra*liberal."
msgstr ""
"Wenn sie kommen, um dir deine Schuhe <i>wegzunehmen</i>, dann vergiss nicht, dass du für sie <i>gearbeitet</i> hast. Ob es dir gefällt oder nicht: Das Tragen dieser Schuhe hat dich liberaler gemacht – <i>ultraliberal</i>."

#. Title = APT ORB / wearing fancy loafers
#. Description = Putting the shoes on gives a one time +1 to Indirect Modes of Taxation, you capitalist swine.
#. Actor = Savoir Faire
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000021000009FB"
msgid "Let's hope no one saw you wearing these outrageously expensive -- and ultraliberal! -- shoes."
msgstr ""
"Hoffen wir mal, dass dich niemand in diesen abscheulich teuren – und ultraliberalen – Schuhen gesehen hat."

#. Title = APT ORB / wearing fancy loafers
#. Description = Putting the shoes on gives a one time +1 to Indirect Modes of Taxation, you capitalist swine.
#. Actor = You
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x0100000400015078"
msgid "Oops, it's a fashion faux pas! [Discard the thought -- and the shoes!]"
msgstr ""
"Ups, das war ein modischer Fauxpas! [Du verwirfst den Gedanken – und entledigst dich der Schuhe!]"

#. Title = APT ORB / wearing fancy loafers
#. Description = Putting the shoes on gives a one time +1 to Indirect Modes of Taxation, you capitalist swine.
#. Actor = Savoir Faire
msgctxt "Dialogue Text/0x01000021000009D0"
msgid "Beautiful things give you a *rush*. It's power -- crafting your style, draping your flesh in silk and leather, deciding how to present yourself to the world."
msgstr ""
"Schöne Dinge geben dir einen <i>Kick</i>. Sie spenden Kraft – prägen deinen Stil, hüllen dein Fleisch in Seide und Leder, entscheiden darüber, wie du dich der Welt präsentierst."
